### Mockapitron

Tool for generating random api response based on

[<img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/cf752a3a210cb265d7aeb4632134b482358c1df6/687474703a2f2f7777772e626f64616d61726b65742e636c2f736d616c6c5f647265616d5f6c6f676f2e706e67">](https://github.com/adleroliveira/dreamjs)

[online](http://api-mockapitron.rhcloud.com/) version [http://api-mockapitron.rhcloud.com/](http://api-mockapitron.rhcloud.com/)

Usage example:

```javascript
fetch('http://api-mockapitron.rhcloud.com/', {
  method: 'post',
  headers: {
    'Accept': 'application/json',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  },
  mode: "cors", 
  body: JSON.stringify({
    schema: {
      name: 'name',
      adress: 'address'
    },
    size: 3
  })
})
.then(function(res){ return res.json() })
.then(function(data){ console.log(data) })
```
